*Meetings will be auto-detected from your calendar during the first briefing run. You can also add them manually.*

## Calendar Matching

{{INSTANCE_NAME}} matches calendar events to meeting folders using `calendar_match` patterns in each home file's YAML frontmatter. Matching is case-insensitive substring matching against event titles.

